'''Yanni Salika''' owns the antique store in [[Shilo Village (location)|Shilo Village]], and is also the starting point for the [[One Small Favour]] quest. He is located north of the river. Yanni will buy many non-tradeable items that are made or gathered during quests, but are of no use after the quest has been completed.

After the completion of [[Shilo Village]], he will buy the [[Tattered scroll]], [[Crumpled scroll]], [[Bervirius notes]], [[Bone key (Shilo Village)|Bone key]], [[Stone-plaque]], [[Locating crystal]], and [[Beads of the dead]]. After the completion of [[Zogre Flesh Eaters]], he will buy the [[Black prism]].

Note that when you ask if he has any interesting items for sale, he will offer to sell back to you the [[Beads of the dead]] (for 1200 coins) or the [[Bone key (Shilo Village)|Bone Key]] (for 100 coins), assuming that you did sell yours to him. He will also sell the player a replacement [[Steel key ring]] if it is lost, though all the keys on it will have to be added again.

